data.title: Austin Powers : the spy who shagged me
data.text:
General Note:

Widescreen version.

DVD-ROM content includes: sample round of Austin Powers operation trivia: Trivia computer game ; The entire Website ... on the DVD! ; Dr. Evil and Austin Powers Web browser and screensavers! ; Three interactive Austin episodes take over your desktop ; Cast, crew and trivia information-continuously updated.

Special features: almost 20 min. deleted scenes; feature length commentary with Mike Meyers, director Jay Roach and co-writer Michael McCullers; behind the scenes documentary; Dr. Evil's "Hidden" special features page: jump to the Dr. Evil song; Comedy Central's canned ham: "The Dr. Evil Story"; music videos: Madonna "Beautiful Stranger"; Lenny Kravitz "American Woman"; Mel B (aka Scary Spice) "Word Up"; four theatrical trailers.

Audio commentary and behind the scenes documentary produced by Mark Rance.
